OL,3,CNew pet abduction law threatens
OL,4,Cthieves with up to five years behind
OL,5,Cbars
OL,7,FA significant rise in pet theft during
OL,8,Fthe pandemic prompted the new law, as
OL,9,FITV News' Lewis Warner reports
OL,11,FThieves targeting people's pets could
OL,12,Fnow be handed a jail sentence of up to
OL,13,Ffive years, a fine, or both, according
OL,14,Fto a new law.
OL,16,FThe Pet Abduction Act 2024, takes
OL,17,Feffect on August 24 in England and
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland, and makes the theft
OL,19,Fof cats and dogs a specific offence.
