OL,3,CNew pet abduction law threatens
OL,4,Cthieves with up to five years behind
OL,5,Cbars
OL,7,FThe stealing of pets previously fell
OL,8,Funder the Theft Act, meaning the legal
OL,9,Fsystem considered the abducted animals
OL,10,Fas stolen property.
OL,12,F"It's dealt with the theft of a dog or
OL,13,Fcat in the same way as if your handbag
OL,14,Fwas stolen, or the theft of a mobile
OL,15,Fphone," solicitor Trevor Cooper told
OL,16,FITV News.
