OL,7,F"Under these new provisions, as it is
OL,8,Fnow regarded a separate offence,
OL,9,Fhopefully the courts will use these
OL,10,Fnew powers that they have available to
OL,11,Fthem."
OL,13,FThe new legislation specifically
OL,14,Freferences cats and dogs, but states
OL,15,Fthat authorities can exercise the
OL,16,Fprovisions in cases involving "animals
OL,17,Fof that species are commonly kept as
OL,18,Fpets".
