OL,7,FNeda Nayyeri is still appealing for
OL,8,Finformation about her two-year-old dog
OL,9,FTeddy, who was stolen from London's
OL,10,FFinsbury Park in June 2024.
OL,12,FSpeaking of her ongoing heartbreak,
OL,13,Fshe said: "Knowing his characteristics
OL,14,Fand his attachments, I worry. It's
OL,15,Flike a family member.
OL,17,F"I'm the caregiver, I feel terrible
OL,18,Fnot being able to care for him right
OL,19,Fnow."
