OL,8,Ffound dog thefts increased between
OL,9,F2022 and 2023, with 2,290 dogs
OL,10,Freported stolen last year
OL,12,FEnglish Bulldogs, French Bulldogs and
OL,13,FXL Bullys were found the be the most
OL,14,Fstolen breeds.
