OL,3,CNew pet abduction law threatens
OL,4,Cthieves with up to five years behind
OL,5,Cbars
OL,7,FThe bill has been promoted by former
OL,8,FConservative MP for Southend West and
OL,9,FLeigh, Anna Firth, who hopes the
OL,10,Fchange could better motivate police.
OL,12,FShe said: "We will finally be able to
OL,13,Fstart building up a proper data set,
OL,14,Fand therefore be able to work out
OL,15,Fwhich police forces are doing this
OL,16,Freally well, which police forces
OL,17,Fperhaps need some support.
OL,19,F"We will actually spread best practice
OL,20,Fand keep our pets safer."
