OL,5,Cbars
OL,7,FDogs Trust has welcomed the
OL,8,Flegislation, praising it for
OL,9,Frecognising pets as "sentient beings"
OL,10,Frather than objects.
OL,12,FPaula Boyden, Veterinary Director at
OL,13,Fthe charity, said: "We are delighted
OL,14,Fto see the Pet Abduction Act come into
OL,15,Fforce, and that it recognises the
OL,16,Femotional bond between dog and owner.
