OL,7,F"For years, Dogs Trust has called for
OL,8,Fharsher penalties to deter those who
OL,9,Fprofit from this despicable crime and
OL,10,Fto tackle the issue of pet theft here
OL,11,Fin the UK."
OL,13,FThe charity advises owners secure
OL,14,Ftheir properties and gardens, never
OL,15,Fleave a dog unattended in public or in
OL,16,Fa car, and make sure pets are
OL,17,Fmicrochipped.
